Servicii adiacente precum : ingrijirea si curatarea spatiilor verzi. 

Ne remarcam prin calitate si flexibilitate, valori de care am dat dovada de-a lungul timpului si care ne-au adus apreciarea clientilor.

For over thirty years, Maintenance of Dallas, Inc.  has developed and refined our procedures to provide the finest in personalized, professional cleaning while serving as stewards for your janitorial dollars.

We are one of the most established building maintenance contractors serving
*office buildings and corporate campuses;
*industrial facilities;
*medical office buildings;
*museums and cultural centers;
*lifestyle and shopping centers;
*educational facilities; and
*houses of worship.

Maintenance of Dallas, Inc.  is recognized in the industry as an innovative leader for establishing safety programs for our employers and tenants. We approach building maintenance from the philosophy that all surfaces should be clean at all times.  We consider frequency schedules to be useful but minimum guidelines for demonstrating uncompromising attention to detail in all areas of our business.

We build enduring relationships with our clients by focusing on excellent service, reliability and integrity.

In every city that we operate, we actively participate in professional associations such as BOMA, to give back to the communities we serve.

City Wide Facility Solutions has become one of the most sought-after service providers in the building maintenance industry. In order to meet the market demand for a holistic approach, City Wide has evolved into a full-service building management company. How we set ourselves apart in the industry:
We offer more than 20 non-janitorial services ranging from high rise window washing to parking lot maintenance;
We “sit on the same side of the table” as the client and represent their needs; We focus on vendor selection, compliance, and overall client satisfaction.

