Nice to meet you, we are Clean Genie!

In a world where first impressions matter, maintaining a clean and organized space has become increasingly important for businesses of all sizes. We understand that every client has different cleaning needs, which is why we work closely with them to develop bespoke cleaning solutions that are tailored to their specific requirements.
From our Headoffice in Bicester, Oxfordshire, and our anothers Franchises for hole England we are perfectly positioned to serve businesses nationwide. We are a Commercial & Industrial cleaning group dedicated to providing the best possible cleaning solutions to businesses across the UK. Our dedicated team operates round the clock, ensuring that we are always available to meet your cleaning needs. We understand that flexibility and reliability are paramount when it comes to maintaining a clean and professional environment. That's why our experienced staff is committed to delivering outstanding service that exceeds your expectations.

Clean Genie has a competitive advantage over other cleaning services because they offer a wide range of services, including:

= Office Cleaning;
- Carpet Cleaning;
- Floor Maintenance;
- Car Showroom Cleaning;
- Pre-Sale and Property Let Cleans;
- School Cleaning;
- Window Cleaning;
- Kitchen and duct Cleaning;
- Graffiti Removal;
- Jet washing cleaning;
- High level cleaning;
- Builders clean; 
- Commercial cleaning;
And more! 

We are also able to provide specialist Rotary Scrubbers, Hot Water Pressure and Steam Cleaning equipment.
So if you’re looking for a reliable and innovative partner to keep your commercial or industrial space clean and safe, look no further than our company. Get in touch with us today to learn more about our services and how we can help you achieve your cleaning goals.
